description:
Armbian 24.5 distribution for ARM devices is out now with support for Orange Pi 5 Pro, Radxa ROCK 5 ITX, and Allwinner T527 Avaota-A1 devices.

The post Armbian 24.5 Released with Orange Pi 5 Pro and Radxa ROCK 5 ITX Support appeared first on 9to5Linux - do not reproduce this article without permission. This RSS feed is intended for readers, not scrapers.
title: Armbian 24.5 Released with Orange Pi 5 Pro and Radxa ROCK 5 ITX Support
